                    <span>From the authors of Eat Smart in Mexico, comes this new title, an easy-to-use menu guide for travelers to Brazil. It contains useful phrases in Portuguese when ordering and a collection of recipes for chefs who want to cook Brazilian fare at home.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Informative & Useful</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
