                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>1999-03-30</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book is an excellent guide to the cuisine of Brazil, which has a vast array of regional specialties, spices, fruits and fish. If you go to the Amazon, Bahia or Rio, for example, you're going to encounter quite different menus. "Eat Smart" is one of my key Brazil guides, along with the music book "The Brazilian Sound."</span>
                  
              
